    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN285-intro">tiṇai, vākai; tuṟai, ...mullai. aricilkiḻār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN285">
<l>pācaṟai yīrē pācaṟai yīrē</l>
<l>tuṭiyaṉ kaiyatu vēlē yaṭipuṇar</l>
<l>vāṅkiru maruppiṟ ṟīntoṭaic cīṟiyāḻp</l>
<l>pāṇaṉ kaiyatu tōlē kāṇvarak</l>
<l>kaṭunteṟṟu mūṭaiyiṉ <gap quantity="9" reason="lost" unit="character"/></l>
<l>vāṭiya mālai malainta ceṉṉiyaṉ</l>
<l>vēntutoḻi layaru maruntalaic cuṟṟamoṭu</l>
<l>neṭunakar vanteṉa viṭukaṇai yocitta</l>
<l>mūri veṇṭōṟ <gap quantity="12" reason="lost" unit="character"/></l>
<l>cēṟupaṭu kurutic cemmaluk kōo</l>
<l>māṟuceṟu neṭuvēṉ mārpuḷam pōka</l>
<l>niṇampoti kaḻaloṭu nilañcērn taṉaṉē</l>
<l>yatukaṇṭu, parantō rellām pukaḻat talaipaṇin</l>
<l>tiṟaiñci yōṉē kurucil piṇaṅkukati</l>
<l>ralamaruṅ kaḻaṉit taṇṇaṭai yoḻiya</l>
<l>vilampā ṭokkaṟ ṟalaivaṟkōr</l>
<l>karampaic cīṟūr nalkiṉa ṉeṉavē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You in the warcamp! Your in the warcamp!</l>
<l>In the hand of the Tuṭi drummer is the spear. In the hand</l>
<l>of the bard with the small lute with sweet strings </l>
<l>[and] a curving big neck, joined to [his] feet, is a shield. So as to be seen,</l>
<l>fast ? grain receptacle….(?)</l>
<l>Because the one with a head that wears a faded garland</l>
<l>has come to the large city with [his] first retinue difficult [to vanquish],</l>
<l>who are engaged in the king’s work, with strong white shields </l>
<l>through which charging arrows have broken, …….</l>
<l>a wealth of blood was spilled, ah, that falls into the mud. </l>
<l>As the opposition-subduing long spear went into [his] chest</l>
<l>he joined the ground along with [his] anklets covered by fat.</l>
<l>Seeing that, while all those who are spread praise, lowering [his] head</l>
<l>he bowed, the lord – so as to say he granted a little village with soil(?)</l>
<l>to the headman equal to poverty,</l>
<l>while the village with paddy fields where intertwined ears are perturbed</l>
<l>stays behind.</l>
</lg>
